name: Mishi Anime
description:
Stable Diffusion 2.1 anime model. Based on a mix of Plat Diffusion, PRMJ, CModel. Then trained on a dataset of quality anime art. The Waifu Diffusion 1.4 kl-f8-anime2 VAE is recommended (already baked into the model).

  • To improve quality add to start of prompt: masterpiece, best quality, high quality, absurdres.

  • Example negative prompt: (worst quality:1.2), low quality, medium quality, deleted, lowres, comic, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry
